hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 对于 $^{87}\text{Rb}$，最大光移为
$$U_{87} \;=\;\frac{\hbar\,\Omega^2}{4\,|\Delta_{87}|}
             \;=\;\frac{\hbar\,\Omega^2}{4\,\Delta_0}
             = U_0\,.$$
因此
$$\hbar\,\Omega^2 = 4\,\Delta_0\,U_0\,.$$

2. 对于 $^{85}\text{Rb}$，失谐为
$$\Delta_{85} = \omega_L - \omega_{85}
             = (\omega_L - \omega_{87}) - (\omega_{85}-\omega_{87})
             = \Delta_{87} - \delta\omega_{iso}
             = -\Delta_0 - \delta\omega_{iso}
             = -\bigl(\Delta_0+\delta\omega_{iso}\bigr)\,.$$
所以
$$|\Delta_{85}| = \Delta_0+\delta\omega_{iso}\,.$$

3. $^{85}\text{Rb}$ 的光移为
$$U_{85}
 = \frac{\hbar\,\Omega^2}{4\,|\Delta_{85}|}
 = \frac{4\,\Delta_0\,U_0}{4\,(\Delta_0+\delta\omega_{iso})}
 = U_0\,\frac{\Delta_0}{\Delta_0+\delta\omega_{iso}}\,.$$

4. 由于 $k_B T = C\,U_{\max}$ 且 $C$ 值相同，
$$\frac{T_{85}}{T_{87}} = \frac{U_{85}}{U_{87}}
                      = \frac{U_0\,\frac{\Delta_0}{\Delta_0+\delta\omega_{iso}}}{U_0}
                      = \frac{\Delta_0}{\Delta_0+\delta\omega_{iso}}\,.$$
因此
$$T_{85} = T_{87}\,\frac{\Delta_0}{\Delta_0+\delta\omega_{iso}}\,.$$
